query:
INSERT INTO admin_email_messages (
            user_id,
            message_id,
            folder_id,
            from_address,
            to_addresses,
            cc_addresses,
            bcc_addresses,
            subject,
            body_text,
            body_html,
            is_read,
            sent_at
        )
        SELECT
            $1, $2, f.id, $3, $4::TEXT[], $5::TEXT[], $6::TEXT[],
            $7, $8, $9, true, $10
        FROM admin_email_folders f
        WHERE f.user_id = $1 AND f.folder_type = 'sent'
